feature_LnhxWG":{"type":"feature","settings":{"heading":"<b>Elegant Design<\/b>","text":"<p>Experience the beauty of restful elegance with our stunning divan bed. Our divan bed boasts a design that seamlessly blends sophistication and style. <\/p>","content_align":"text-start","hotspot_x":28,"hotspot_y":29}},"feature_8zgnca":{"type":"feature","settings":{"heading":"<b>Durable & Strong Base<\/b>","text":"<p>Our divan bed features a durable and robust divan base with drawers. Engineered for strength and longevity, our divan bed provides a solid foundation that stands the test of time. <\/p>","content_align":"text-start","hotspot_x":65,"hotspot_y":73}},"feature_FhLJ9f":{"type":"feature","settings":{"heading":"<b>Extra Storage Space<\/b>","text":"<p>Maximize your bedroom space with our divan bed featuring a divan base with drawers for seamless storage solutions. Our thoughtfully designed bed combines comfort with practicality, offering built-in drawers to effortlessly declutter your space. Experience the perfect blend of style and functionality as you tuck away blankets, linens, or personal items in our king size divan bed with storage.<\/p>","content_align":"text-start","hotspot_x":37,"hotspot_y":73}}},"block_order":["feature_LnhxWG","feature_8zgnca","feature_FhLJ9f"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"product":"","show_content":true,"layout":"text_first","text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"heading_size":"h1","enlarge_text":false,"title":"Redefine Comfort With BedroomKing","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","hotspot_color":"#070707","color_scheme":"none","button_style":"btn btn--primary"}},"rich_text_FgrRj6":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":true,"color_scheme":"none","full_width":true,"prevent_animation":false}},"rich_text_Kpk3XR":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"subheading_3DwFy3":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"text":"The Ultimate Sleeping Experience"}},"heading_tgig9x":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Key Features of BedroomKing TV Beds","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}}},"block_order":["subheading_3DwFy3","heading_tgig9x"],"settings":{"text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":true,"color_scheme":"1","full_width":true,"prevent_animation":false}},"media_with_text_WrKJxt":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_HaCXmN":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Wireless Remote Control","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_PUabAj":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Experience the epitome of modern comfort with our TV Bed featuring wireless remote control for the TV lift system. Our King Size TV Bed can be easily controlled with this remote, customizing your viewing experience with precision and ease. Elevate your bedroom aesthetics and relaxation levels with our TV bed with remote.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_HaCXmN","text_PUabAj"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/m.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_UetF78":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_ryz3zp":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Integrate Your Own TV","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_UH9aRP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Elevate your bedroom with our versatile TV Bed that lets you integrate your own TV up to 47 inches. This customizable feature allows you to personalize your entertainment space. Our bed with TV and storage ensures a seamless blend of your chosen TV size with the elegant design of our TV bed.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_ryz3zp","text_UH9aRP"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/111.jpg","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_RMtjiR":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_XdrNzz":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Customizable Mattress","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_D4j7Rz":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Experience the epitome of personalized sleep with our TV bed with Mattress. Tailor your sleep sanctuary by selecting the perfect mattress for your TV bed. Our Super king TV Beds also come with the option of an orthopedic mattress.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_XdrNzz","text_D4j7Rz"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/NEST_MATTRESS_PILE.jpg","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_cBUcgr":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_kttBV3":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Storage Space","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_krxTXP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Maximize your bedroom's functionality with our TV bed featuring extra storage space. Keep your belongings neatly organized and out of sight while enjoying the comfort and style of our premium king size TV bed. Transform your bedroom today with our double tv bed with storage<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_kttBV3","text_krxTXP"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Kaydian-Titan-TV-Bed-With-Ottoman-Storage-Slate-Fabric-6ft-Super-Kingsize_700_600_9OF1I.jpg","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"slideshow_3e3jXr":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_Fxpe39":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1800_X_900_8_18.png","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shopify_Mobile_portrait_15.png","url":"","overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"subheading":"","heading":"","heading_size":"h0","heading_h1":false,"text":"","enlarge_text":true,"button_1_label":"","button_1_link":"","button_1_style":"btn btn--primary","button_2_label":"","button_2_link":"","button_2_style":"btn btn--primary","transparent_content_color":"#ffffff","countdown_show":false,"countdown_end_date":"","countdown_end_time":"","countdown_end_text":"","enlarge_end_text":false,"countdown_hide_on_end":false,"use_custom_colors":false,"count_color":"#ffffff","bg_color":"#070707","bg_grad":""}}},"block_order":["slide_Fxpe39"],"settings":{"height_mode":"auto","fixed_height_desktop":600,"fixed_height_mobile":350,"mobile_stacked":false,"nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","pagination_color":"#ffffff","nav_position":"justify-center","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":true,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"white","full_width":true,"tint_color":"#000000","tint_opacity":0,"accessibility_info":"","prevent_animation":true}},"multi_column_kiEndT":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_Ed3rL4":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/mkm.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<h2>One Year Warranty<\/h2><p>Our TV bed comes with a comprehensive 12-month warranty, offering you peace of mind and assurance in the quality of our products. Experience superior craftsmanship with the added security of our warranty, ensuring your satisfaction with our TV Bed.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_nh3dgA":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/232.jpg","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<h2>Premium Fabric Options<\/h2><p>Personalize your <strong>TV Bed<\/strong> with a choice of premium fabric options. Select from a range of luxurious materials and colors to complement your bedroom decor, ensuring your <strong>Super king TV Bed<\/strong> is not only functional but also a stylish centerpiece.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_Ed3rL4","column_nh3dgA"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-start","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"grid","column_size":"large","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"1","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"testimonials_k78Di3":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_twi4ep":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Our TV bed has transformed family movie nights!<br\/>The kids love it, and we appreciate the quality family time it brings. The bed itself is comfortable, and the TV adds a unique touch to our bedroom. It's a hit in our household, and we highly recommend it to other families.<\/p>","author":"Lisa Johnson","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_Pmtnra":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>I absolutely love my TV bed! The integrated TV system works like a charm, and the convenience of having it right there in the footboard is fantastic. The bed is not only stylish but also very comfortable. The whole setup has exceeded my expectations!<\/p>","author":"Michael Chen","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_DkmHBc":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>From the moment we received our TV bed, it felt like a slice of luxury in our bedroom. The TV integration is seamless, and the quality of the materials is top-notch. Every night feels like a trip to a high-end hotel. Couldn't be happier with our purchase!\"<\/p>","author":"Shen Anna","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}}},"block_order":["testimonial_twi4ep","testimonial_Pmtnra","testimonial_DkmHBc"],"settings":{"heading":"CUSTOMER RAVES","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h4","text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center justify-center","nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":false,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"1","full_width":true}},"recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","settings":{"heading":"YOU MAY ALSO LIKE","heading_align":"text-center","layout":"carousel","card_size_mobile":"large","card_size":"medium","products_to_show":8}},"faq_K9VnUr":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_kQgbqx":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What is a TV Bed?","text":"<p>A TV bed is a bed that has the capacity built into the frame to house your television. The TV can be hidden away in the foot of the bed, and then exposed at the touch of a button, which is perfect for decluttering your bedroom and helps you to maximize the space available<\/p>"}},"question_3Pe7hU":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"How do TV beds plug in?","text":"<p>All of the internal wires and leads are hidden inside the bed frame. To plug your TV bed into the mains, an extension lead may be required to reach the television plug beneath the bed, depending on how far away your plug socket is. Our beds come with a UK 3 pin plug fitting.<\/p>"}},"question_CDYKzb":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Is a TV included inevery TV Bed?","text":"<p>No, a TV is not included in our TV Bed. However, you have the flexibility to integrate your own TV, and our TV Beds support screens up to 47 inches. This allows you to personalize your entertainment experience and choose a TV that suits your preferences.<\/p>"}},"question_UQXUea":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Will you install and deliver my TV Bed for me?","text":"<p>Absolutely! Our delivery team ensures your TV Bed is delivered directly to your room of choice. For added convenience, installation services are available across the UK at a small additional charge. We strive to make the entire process seamless, providing you with a hassle-free experience.<\/p>"}},"question_ARyiFj":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"This is quite a big purchase — can I spread the costs?","text":"<p>Yes, we understand that purchasing a TV Bed is a significant investment. To make it more accessible, we offer a range of interest-free options. You have the flexibility to spread the cost of your purchase, ensuring that you can enjoy the luxury and comfort of our TV Beds without financial strain.<\/p>"}},"question_aPd8UA":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Can I use my existing plasma or LED TV with a new TV Bed?","text":"<p>Absolutely! Our TV Beds are designed to accommodate your existing plasma or LED TV, up to 47 inches in size. This feature allows you to seamlessly integrate your current entertainment setup with the new TV Bed, providing you with continuity and flexibility.<\/p>"}},"question_Wqyf8F":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Do you sell TV Beds with under bed storage?","text":"<p>Yes, we have an extensive range of TV Beds that not only offer the luxury of entertainment but also come with full under bed storage. This clever design maximizes the functionality of your bedroom, providing ample space to keep your belongings neatly organized and out of sight.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_kQgbqx","question_3Pe7hU","question_CDYKzb","question_UQXUea","question_ARyiFj","question_aPd8UA","question_Wqyf8F"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","heading_align":"text-center","color_scheme":"1","full_width":true}},"slideshow_Dte3JH":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_dMcLcH":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Gift_Banner_Size_2_15.png","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Gift_Banner_Size_2_16.png","url":"","overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"subheading":"","heading":"","heading_size":"h0","heading_h1":false,"text":"","enlarge_text":true,"button_1_label":"","button_1_link":"","button_1_style":"btn btn